00:08.074 --> 00:09.974
That's okay, Woody.
Yep.

00:10.043 --> 00:13.045
Had to make another embarrassing
trip to the drug store

00:13.112 --> 00:15.613
to get a little, uh...

00:15.681 --> 00:17.982
Protection?
Yeah.

00:18.051 --> 00:20.852
You know, Kelly and I want
to have a family and all,

00:20.853 --> 00:23.555
but we figured we'd
wait until after that raise you promised.

00:23.556 --> 00:26.358
Hope you got a lot
of protection.

00:26.359 --> 00:28.543
Well, as usual, you know,
I'm a little embarrassed

00:28.544 --> 00:30.212
and nervous when I go in there,

00:30.279 --> 00:32.214
