00:37.019 --> 00:40.455
Yeah. So I got some
paper plates...

00:40.522 --> 00:42.924
batteries, flashbulbs,

00:42.992 --> 00:45.327
Skol...

00:45.394 --> 00:47.996
some gum...

00:48.064 --> 00:51.833
