00:51.901 --> 00:53.969
oh, eyeglass repair kit...

00:54.036 --> 00:56.171
Yeah.

00:56.239 --> 00:58.606
Oh, notebook paper...

00:58.708 --> 01:01.242
and... VO5.

01:01.310 --> 01:02.844
Where's the, uh...

01:02.912 --> 01:04.879
